AFFILIATE WEBSITE TEMPLATE

Our Classic Template is ideal for building affiliate marketing websites that need advanced sharing channels, powerful insights, referral rewards, and payment methods.

This affiliate marketing website is built with Bootstrap 4 Framework, HTML5, CSS3, and JQuery. It is supported in 7 languages, is easily customizable, fully responsive, and supports all current browsers and devices.

AFFILIATE PAYMENT METHODS

Multiple affiliate marketing payment methods are available on this affiliate website template, and you can activate more than one to allow your affiliates to choose their preferred payment method. Since affiliates love to get paid in cash, PayPal payouts, e-gift cards, and bank transfers are your best affiliate payment method options when building an affiliate marketing template.
